      "target_text": "这事别让别人知道。",
      "quality": 0.84,
      "tags": [
        "secret"
      ]
    },
    {
      "source_text": "I can live with that.",
      "target_text": "这样我能接受。",
      "quality": 0.84,
      "tags": [
        "agreement"
      ]
    },
    {
      "source_text": "That was uncalled for.",
      "target_text": "你刚才那话太过了。",
      "quality": 0.84,
      "tags": [
        "conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "source_text": "Take it down a notch.",
      "target_text": "冷静点。",
      "quality": 0.84,
      "tags": [
        "conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "source_text": "I said what I said.",
      "target_text": "我话就放这儿了。",
      "quality": 0.84,
      "tags": [
        "conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "source_text": "Don't make this weird.",
      "target_text": "别把气氛搞尴尬。",
      "quality": 0.84,
      "tags": [
        "colloquial"
      ]
    },
    {
      "source_text": "You're overthinking it.",
      "target_text": "你想太多了。",
      "quality": 0.84,
      "tags": [
        "dialogue"
      ]
    },
    {
      "source_text": "I have a bad feeling about this.",
      "target_text": "我有种不好的预感。",
      "quality": 0.84,
      "tags": [
        "suspense"
      ]
    },
    {
      "source_text": "This is getting out of hand.",
      "target_text": "事情快失控了。",
      "quality": 0.84,
      "tags": [
        "conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "source_text": "I am not in the mood.",
      "target_text": "我现在没心情。",
      "quality": 0.84,
      "tags": [
        "dialogue"
      ]
    },
    {
      "source_text": "I'm not proud of it.",
      "target_text": "这事我也不光彩。",
      "quality": 0.84,
      "tags": [
        "confession"
      ]
    },
    {
      "source_text": "It slipped out.",
      "target_text": "我一不小心说漏嘴了。",
      "quality": 0.84,
      "tags": [
        "dialogue"
      ]
    },
    {
      "source_text": "You made your point.",
      "target_text": "你的意思我明白了。",
      "quality": 0.84,
      "tags": [
        "dialogue"
      ]
    },
    {
      "source_text": "Let's call it a night.",
      "target_text": "今晚就到这吧。",
      "quality": 0.84,
      "tags": [
        "party"
      ]
    },
    {
      "source_text": "I'm all ears.",
