      "quality": 0.84,
      "tags": [
        "sarcasm"
      ]
    },
    {
      "source_text": "Let's keep it moving.",
      "target_text": "别耽误了，继续吧。",
      "quality": 0.84,
      "tags": [
        "dialogue"
      ]
    },
    {
      "source_text": "I was getting to that.",
      "target_text": "我正要说到这点。",
      "quality": 0.84,
      "tags": [
        "dialogue"
      ]
    },
    {
      "source_text": "That is beside the point.",
