      "quality": 0.84,
      "tags": [
        "subtitle",
        "colloquial"
      ]
    },
    {
      "source_text": "That sounds personal.",
      "target_text": "听起来像私人恩怨。",
      "quality": 0.84,
      "tags": [
        "subtitle",
        "colloquial"
      ]
    },
    {
      "source_text": "It feels different this time.",
      "target_text": "这次感觉不一样。",
      "quality": 0.84,
      "tags": [
        "subtitle",
        "colloquial"
      ]
    },
    {
      "source_text": "It feels too easy.",
      "target_text": "这也太顺利了。",
      "quality": 0.84,
      "tags": [
        "subtitle",
        "colloquial"
      ]
    },
    {
      "source_text": "It feels like a setup.",
      "target_text": "感觉像有人设了局。",
      "quality": 0.84,
      "tags": [
        "subtitle",
        "colloquial"
      ]
    },
    {
      "source_text": "Let's not make a scene.",
      "target_text": "别当众闹起来。",
      "quality": 0.84,
      "tags": [
        "subtitle",
        "colloquial"
      ]
    },
    {
      "source_text": "Let's not push our luck.",
      "target_text": "别再碰运气了。",
      "quality": 0.84,
      "tags": [
        "subtitle",
        "colloquial"
      ]
